  "title": "More Beautiful Buttons",
  "description": "Buttons in more colors to bring beauty to your world",
  "body": "<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/633/748/bh_mbb_header.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1142\" height=\"367\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"featherlight-image featherlight-inner\" src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/633/746/bh_mbb_buttons.png\" alt=\"Buttons\" width=\"1142\" height=\"123\" /></p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/thumbnails/213/970/310/172/phase-ii.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"273\" height=\"172\" /></p>\n<p>Over 200 buttons for pressing pleasure! Some buttons sound like sand, others like glass, some like wood, and yet others sound wet! Can you craft them all?</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/thumbnails/213/921/310/172/buttons-phase-i.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"225\" height=\"172\" /></p>\n<p>These buttons want to be pressed by you and only you.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/thumbnails/214/188/310/172/9-of-the-113-new-buttons.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"182\" height=\"172\" /></p>\n<p>Gold, Iron, Diamond, Lapis, Glass, Emerald, &hellip;</p>\n<h2>Crafting</h2>\n<p>Combine any block with a button press and get your very own button version of that block. A button press is crafted with 8 sticks in a chest pattern.</p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/214/214/recipe-format.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"249\" height=\"133\" /></p>\n<h2>Want 200+ Giant Buttons?</h2>\n<p>Yeah, you know you do. So, head on over to&nbsp;<a href=\"https://minecraft.curseforge.com/projects/big-beautiful-buttons\"><strong>Big Beautiful Buttons</strong></a>&nbsp;and get to pressing those massively enormous buttons.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/633/747/bh_mbb_community.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://discordapp.com/api/guilds/96753964485181440/widget.png?style=banner2\" /> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/kreezxil\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://s12.directupload.net/images/200916/joj33k55.png\" /></a> <a href=\"https://www.reddit.com/r/MinecraftModdedForge\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://s12.directupload.net/images/200916/efhmdjhg.png\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://bisecthosting.com/kreezxil\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/633/750/bh_mbb_promo.png\" alt=\"Bisect Hosting\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">If you want a server setup for the Any mod pack with zero effort, get a <a href=\"https://bisecthosting.com/kreezxil\">server with BisectHosting</a> and receive 25% off your first month as a new customer using the code kreezxil</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Modpacks</h2>\n<p>Yes, you can use my mod in your pack.</p>\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>",
